used commands in a contextual menu

00:16:56.690 --> 00:16:56.690
on your files or folders or objects
and again support the user and

00:16:56.690 --> 00:16:56.690
different user styles in interacting.

00:16:56.690 --> 00:16:56.690
So try to keep the interface flexible.

